overview: OLIVIA NEWTON JOHN Soul Kiss (Very scarce 1985 Japanese NTSC stereo 5-track laser disc, including Soul Kiss, superb picture sleeve design with illustrated lyric insert & obi-strip, still in the original open shrink). Includes a 2-side insert with lyrics in English and Japanese, with interview sections of Olivia Newton-John between each title. Tracklist:  -Soul Kiss  -Culture Shock  -Emotional Tangle  -Toughen Up  -The Right Moment
title: Olivia Newton-John: Soul Kiss
